summary: Five halloween make-up warpaints: Cat, Witch, Doll, Clown, Skull
descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod so don't judge me too harshly xD
To use the warpaints you will need RaceMenu mod
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?

There are five character make-up warpaints in the pack:
1. Clown - 1,2,3 (combination between first, second and third warpaint)
2. Cat - 4,5 (use black lip color with them)
3. Doll - 6,7
4. Witch - 8,9
5. Skull - 10

Installation:

Use NMM or unpack it in skyrim main folder
author: Dob1
